4/AJR.15.15016">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.2214/AJR.13.12421"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.13.12421">Gastrointestinal Tract Filling Defects in Pediatric Patients</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Patricia T. Chang</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Edward Y. Lee</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ricardo Restrepo</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ronald L. Eisenberg</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2014Jul1 | American Journal of Roentgenology, Vol. 203, No. 1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.13.12421">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-88-470-5489-9_19"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-88-470-5489-9_19">S</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Pasquale Paolantonio</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Clarisse Dromain</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">24 August 2013</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-88-470-5489-9_19">Crossref</a></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div>
